{"@class": "com.nd.elearning.sdk.resource.gateway.v5.bean.question.QuestionVo", "original_type": 4, "original_sub_type": "questions", "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "id": "b8e324a1-75a4-4e69-b2bb-f271693074f4", "type": 201, "content": {"preview": {"question_big": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/b8e324a1-75a4-4e69-b2bb-f271693074f4@5.pkg/1772602112834/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772602113209", "question_small": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/b8e324a1-75a4-4e69-b2bb-f271693074f4@5.pkg/1772602112834/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772602113209"}, "identifier": "b8e324a1-75a4-4e69-b2bb-f271693074f4", "feedbacks": [{"identifier": "showHint", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": ""}, {"identifier": "showAnswer", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<p>选项A“四楞”：“楞” 应写作 “棱” ，表示物体上不同方向的两个平面连接的部分 ；“待立” 应写作 “侍立” ，指恭敬地站在旁边侍候 。所以A选项字形错误。<br />\n选项B“属咐”：正确写法是 “嘱咐” ，“嘱” 意为告诉对方记住应该怎样，不应该怎样 。所以B选项字形错误。<br />\n选项C“篾片（miè）”：“篾” 指劈成条的竹片 ，读音正确。“砒霜（pī）”：“砒” 是一种无机化合物，读音无误。“宝钗（chāi）”：“钗” 是妇女的一种首饰 ，读音正确。“李纨（wán）”：“纨” 读音正确 。该选项字音、字形均正确。<br />\n选项D“发怔（zhèng）”：“怔” 在这里表示发愣、发呆 ，读音错误，应为zhèng ；“揣水” 应写作 “搋水” ，“搋” 有用手按压、揉弄等意思 。所以D选项字音、字形都有错误。</p>\n"}], "sequnce_number": 1, "description": "<p>1.下列词语字音、字形完全正确的一项是（　　）</p>\n", "title": "1.下列词语字音、字形完全正确的一项是（　　）", "res_type": "$RE0201", "adaptive": false, "timer": {"timer_type": "sequence"}, "time_dependent": false, "responses": [{"identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "1-1", "base_type": "identifier", "cardinality": "single", "corrects": ["C"]}], "location": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/b8e324a1-75a4-4e69-b2bb-f271693074f4@5.pkg/item.json?v=1750747453787", "items": [{"min_choices": 0, "attachments": [], "columns": 1, "type": "choice", "choices_list": [], "associable_hotspots": [], "children": [], "hide_answer_area": false, "options": [], "orientation": 0, "multiple": false, "raw": false, "titles": [], "rows": 1, "response_identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "0", "max_choices": 1, "gap_imgs": [], "choice_type": "character", "shuffle": false, "choices": [{"identifier": "A", "correct": false, "match_max": 1, "group_id": "", "fixed": false, "text": "<p>四楞（lèng）撮弄（cuō）调停（tiáo）待立（shì）</p>\n"}, {"identifier": "B", "correct": false, "match_max": 1, "group_id": "", "fixed": false, "text": "<p>银箸（zhù）俺们（ǎn）筵席（yàn）属咐（zhǔ）</p>\n"}, {"identifier": "C", "correct": false, "match_max": 1, "group_id": "", "fixed": false, "text": "<p>篾片（miè）砒霜（pī）宝钗（chāi）李纨（wán）</p>\n"}, {"identifier": "D", "correct": false, "match_max": 1, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<p>发怔（zhēng）镶银（xiāng）岔气（chà）揣水（duān）</p>\n"}], "prompt": "<p>1.下列词语字音、字形完全正确的一项是（　　）</p>\n", "object": {"data": "", "width": "1000", "type": "image/png", "params": {"originalImage": "", "blankImage": ""}, "height": "600"}}], "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878"}, "source": {"container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "tags": ["$M002000000", "44bee8bc-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "6a749654-0772-11ed-ac74-092ab92074e6", "44bec0c6-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "5036342747", "$RE0000", "$M003002000", "ff8080814371757b014390f883db0453", "$RE0200", "$RE0201", "e7bbce2c-0590-11ed-9c79-92fc3b3249d5", "44bee8bc-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "6a749654-0772-11ed-ac74-092ab92074e6", "44bec0c6-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "ff8080814371757b014390f883db0453", "e7bbce2c-0590-11ed-9c79-92fc3b3249d5"], "status": "ONLINE", "is_publish": false, "id": "b8e324a1-75a4-4e69-b2bb-f271693074f4", "global_title": {"zh-CN": "1.下列词语字音、字形完全正确的一项是（　　）"}, "global_description": {"zh-CN": "<p>1.下列词语字音、字形完全正确的一项是（　　）</p>\n"}, "global_keywords": {}, "global_label": {}, "custom_properties": {"sys_packing_status": "ready", "preview": {"question_big": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/b8e32